{"script": {"id": "video_script_imagination_001", "topic": "英语词汇教学:imagination", "description": "通过词根词缀法讲解imagination,掌握其构词规律及相关词汇", "targetAudience": "英语学习者", "totalDuration": 91, "scenes": [{"id": "scene_001", "type": "title", "content": {"type": "title", "mainTitle": "imagination", "subtitle": "想象力的力量"}, "narration": "今天我们要学习一个非常重要的单词——imagination,也就是想象力.这个词汇在英语中使用频率很高,无论是在日常生活还是学术写作中都非常常见.让我们一起来深入了解这个词吧.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 18, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_001_e3b2f9.wav", "audioDuration": 16.8}, {"id": "scene_002", "type": "vocabulary-card", "content": {"type": "vocabulary-card", "phrase": "imagination", "pronunciation": "/ɪˌmædʒɪˈneɪʃən/", "partOfSpeech": "noun", "definitions": ["想象力；幻想力", "想象；幻觉", "创造力；独创性"]}, "narration": "首先让我们来看一下这个词的基本信息.Imagination是一个名词,发音为诶马吉内顺.它的主要含义有三个方面:第一是指想象力或幻想力；第二是指想象这种心理活动本身,也就是在脑海中形成图像的过程；第三还可以表示创造力或独创性.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 23, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_002_101209.wav", "audioDuration": 22.0}, {"id": "scene_003", "type": "highlight", "content": {"type": "highlight", "sentence": "imagination = imag- (image图像) + -in- + -ation (名词后缀)", "highlights": [{"text": "imag-", "color": "#FFD93D", "label": "词根"}, {"text": "-ation", "color": "#6BCB77", "label": "后缀"}], "images": [{"url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/1274260/pexels-photo-1274260.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "alt": "A silhouette hand holds a mason jar capturing a stunning galaxy under a starry night sky.", "position": "right", "size": "medium"}], "rootAffix": [{"root": "imag-", "meaning": "源自拉丁语imago,意为图像、影像", "label": "词根", "narration": "词根imag-来源于拉丁语imago,本意是图像或影像.这个词根传达了在脑海中形成画面或形象的概念.当我们使用想象力时,实际上就是在内心构建图像的过程.", "relatedWords": [{"word": "image", "meaning": "图像,影像", "highlight": "imag-", "narration": "image,图像", "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/rw_image_6422.wav", "audioDuration": 1.9}, {"word": "imagine", "meaning": "想象,设想", "highlight": "imagin-", "narration": "imagine,想象", "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/rw_imagine_d818.wav", "audioDuration": 2.0}, {"word": "imaginative", "meaning": "富有想象力的", "highlight": "imagin-", "narration": "imaginative,富有想象力的", "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/rw_imaginative_a090.wav", "audioDuration": 2.8}], "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/root_imag-_609c.wav", "audioDuration": 15.8}, {"root": "-ation", "meaning": "表示行为、过程或状态的名词后缀", "label": "后缀", "narration": "后缀-ation是常见的名词后缀,表示某种行为的过程或状态.将imag-加上-ation,就构成了表示想象这种心理活动过程的名词imagination.", "relatedWords": [{"word": "creation", "meaning": "创造,创造物", "highlight": "-ation", "narration": "creation,创造", "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/rw_creation_b54c.wav", "audioDuration": 1.9}, {"word": "education", "meaning": "教育", "highlight": "-ation", "narration": "education,教育", "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/rw_education_8ece.wav", "audioDuration": 2.2}], "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/root_-ation_907c.wav", "audioDuration": 14.3}]}, "narration": "现在让我们深入了解这个词的词根词缀结构.Imagination这个词可以拆解为imag-加上-ation两部分.词根imag-来源于拉丁语,表示图像或影像的意思；后缀-ation是名词后缀,表示某种行为的过程或状态.这样的构词分析能帮助我们更好地记忆和理解这个单词.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 67, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_003_c1ce09.wav", "audioDuration": 22.8}, {"id": "scene_004", "type": "example", "content": {"type": "example", "english": "Children have boundless imagination and can create entire worlds in their minds.", "chinese": "孩子们拥有无限的想象力,能够在脑海中创造出整个世界.", "highlights": [{"text": "imagination", "color": "#FFD93D"}], "images": [{"url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/7105833/pexels-photo-7105833.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "alt": "Homemade cardboard rocket ship wrapped in foil in a sunny park setting, symbolizing creativity and play.", "position": "center", "size": "medium"}], "englishAudioUrl": "/audio/tts/example_en_scene_004_53ebab.wav", "englishAudioDuration": 6.2}, "narration": "Children have boundless imagination and can create entire worlds in their minds. 意思是:孩子们拥有无限的想象力,能够在脑海中创造出整个世界.这个例句展示了imagination的第一层含义,强调其无边无际的特性以及创造力.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 26, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_004_208bea.wav", "audioDuration": 19.4}, {"id": "scene_005", "type": "example", "content": {"type": "example", "english": "The author's vivid imagination brings the fictional characters to life in a remarkable way.", "chinese": "作者生动的想象力以非凡的方式将小说中的人物形象栩栩如生地呈现出来.", "highlights": [{"text": "imagination", "color": "#FFD93D"}], "images": [{"url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/3847626/pexels-photo-3847626.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "alt": "From above view of set of various classic novels with colorful images on covers placed on white marble surface", "position": "center", "size": "medium"}], "englishAudioUrl": "/audio/tts/example_en_scene_005_a2b10e.wav", "englishAudioDuration": 6.6}, "narration": "The author's vivid imagination brings the fictional characters to life in a remarkable way. 意思是:作者生动的想象力以非凡的方式将小说中的人物形象栩栩如生地呈现出来.这个例句则展示了imagination在创作领域中的应用,体现了其与创造力和艺术表达之间的紧密联系.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 30, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_005_d1a3a7.wav", "audioDuration": 22.6}, {"id": "scene_006", "type": "summary", "content": {"type": "summary", "points": ["imagination是名词,意为想象力、创造力或幻想", "词根imag-来源于拉丁语imago,表示图像或影像", "后缀-ation表示行为或状态的过程", "相关词汇包括:image(图像)、imagine(想象)、imaginative(富有想象力的)、imaginary(虚构的)"]}, "narration": "现在让我们回顾今天学到的内容.Imagination是一个表示想象力或创造力的名词.它的词根imag-来源于拉丁语,表示图像的意思,这与想象活动中形成心理图像的本质相吻合.后缀-ation则表示某种过程或状态.最后,掌握相关词汇如image、imagine、imaginative和imaginary,能帮助我们更全面地理解这个词族.希望今天的讲解对你的英语学习有所帮助！", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 30, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_006_7f494f.wav", "audioDuration": 34.7}]}, "audioUrls": {"scene_001_narration": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\narration_scene_001_e3b2f9.wav", "scene_002_narration": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\narra